Project Overview :
This project is an interactive Microsoft Excel dashboard built to analyze e-commerce sales and customer data. It transforms raw sales data into meaningful business insights using Excel's data analysis and visualization features.

Features :
Cleaned and organized raw sales data
Created Pivot Tables for data summarization
Designed an interactive dashboard with KPIs
Visualized sales performance using charts
Analyzed customer ratings and payment methods
Identified monthly sales trends and product performance

Dashboard KPIs :
Total Revenue
Total Orders
Total Quantity Sold
Average Customer Rating

Analysis Included :
Sales by Product
Sales by Category
Monthly Sales Trend
Payment Method Analysis
Customer Rating Analysis

Tools Used :
Microsoft Excel
Pivot Tables
Pivot Charts
Excel Formulas
Data Cleaning
Data Visualization
Dashboard Design

Skills Demonstrated :
Data Cleaning
Data Analysis
Business Intelligence
Dashboard Development
Data Visualization
Reporting

Outcome :
The dashboard provides a clear overview of sales performance and customer behavior, enabling quick business insights and better decision-making.

